@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_jrbpun(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.sin(wp.abs((tmp + 0.51 / v0 + 0.95)))
    tmp = (v1 * 0.13)
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.cos(wp.cos(v1 + 0.01)))
    v2 = wp.exp(wp.cos((tmp + 0.66 / tmp + 0.68)))
    v0 = v1
    data[tid] = v0
